text.section:
The membership of any person in the system shall cease:
Upon withdrawal of his accumulated account balance at or any time after termination of employment, regardless of length of service;
Upon disability retirement;
Upon service retirement;
Upon death;
For persons hired prior to August 1, 2000, upon termination of employment with prejudice; or
For persons hired on or after August 1, 2000, upon conviction of a felony relating to the person's employment as provided in subsection (3) of this section.
